## Phase 2: Core Features (Months 4-6)

### Objectives:
- Implement star earning system
- Add coin conversion mechanism
- Deploy charity trigger (₹50,000 threshold)

### Key Deliverables:
```javascript
const phase2 = {
  starSystem: {
    earning: {
      dailyLogin: 10,
      eventParticipation: 50,
      referral: 100,
      contentCreation: 25
    },
    conversion: {
      rate: 10, // 10 stars = 1 coin
      minimum: 50000
    }
  },
  charityTrigger: {
    threshold: 50000,
    percentage: 1.0, // 100% above threshold
    automatic: true,
    immutable: true
  },
  payout: {
    processingTime: "5 minutes",
    availability: "24/7",
    methods: ["Bank Transfer", "UPI", "Crypto"]
  }
};
```

### Implementation:
```javascript
// Star to Coin Conversion
function convertStarsToCoins(stars) {
  const CONVERSION_RATE = 10;
  const MIN_STARS = 50000;
  
  if (stars < MIN_STARS) {
    return { success: false, message: "Minimum 50,000 stars required" };
  }
  
  return {
    success: true,
    coins: Math.floor(stars / CONVERSION_RATE),
    remainingStars: stars % CONVERSION_RATE
  };
}

// Charity Trigger
function processCharityTrigger(earnings) {
  const THRESHOLD = 50000;
  
  if (earnings <= THRESHOLD) {
    return { userAmount: earnings, charityAmount: 0 };
  }
  
  return {
    userAmount: THRESHOLD,
    charityAmount: earnings - THRESHOLD,
    triggered: true
  };
}
```

### Success Criteria:
- [ ] Star earning system live
- [ ] Coin conversion functional
- [ ] Charity trigger tested and deployed
- [ ] 10,000+ active users

